description: Cymat Technologies Ltd., a materials technology company, manufactures and sells stabilized aluminum foam products worldwide. The company provides architectural materials under the Alusion brand name; and automotive and blast mitigation products under the SmartMetal brand name. It serves defense and military, automotive and transportation, architectural, and other application. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Mississauga, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Michael M. Liik MBA, P. Eng, P.Eng.
